-- Thales Plans Cost Cuts of 10% to 15% Over Two Years, La Tribune Reports
-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 2010-10-06T04:27:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-06/thales-plans-cost-cuts-of-10-to-15-over-two-years-la-tribune-reports.html
Thales SA is seeking cost cuts of
between 10 percent and 15 percent across all divisions over the
2011-12 period, French daily La Tribune reported, citing
unidentified people.  Management has summoned unions for talks over job cuts, the
newspaper said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  